[
    {
        "text": "In the biblical story of the Tower of Babel,...",
        "startTime": 7025,
        "endTime": 9451,
        "slowStartTime": 10687,
        "slowEndTime": 14402
    },
    {
        "text": "...all of humanity once spoke a single language...",
        "startTime": 9641,
        "endTime": 12264,
        "slowStartTime": 14611,
        "slowEndTime": 18621
    },
    {
        "text": "...until they suddenly split into many groups unable to understand each other.",
        "startTime": 12373,
        "endTime": 16223,
        "slowStartTime": 18709,
        "slowEndTime": 24560
    },
    {
        "text": "We don't really know if such an original language ever existed,...",
        "startTime": 17042,
        "endTime": 20168,
        "slowStartTime": 25713,
        "slowEndTime": 30477
    },
    {
        "text": "...but we do know that the thousands of languages existing today...",
        "startTime": 20453,
        "endTime": 23561,
        "slowStartTime": 30830,
        "slowEndTime": 35567
    },
    {
        "text": "...can be traced back to a much smaller number.",
        "startTime": 23687,
        "endTime": 26052,
        "slowStartTime": 35681,
        "slowEndTime": 39303
    },
    {
        "text": "So, how did we end up with so many?",
        "startTime": 26763,
        "endTime": 28436,
        "slowStartTime": 40294,
        "slowEndTime": 42879
    },
    {
        "text": "In the early days of human migration, the world was much less populated.",
        "startTime": 29333,
        "endTime": 33157,
        "slowStartTime": 44150,
        "slowEndTime": 49961
    },
    {
        "text": "Groups of people that shared a single language and culture often split into smaller tribes,...",
        "startTime": 33788,
        "endTime": 38135,
        "slowStartTime": 50832,
        "slowEndTime": 57427
    },
    {
        "text": "...going separate ways in search of fresh game and fertile land.",
        "startTime": 38439,
        "endTime": 41309,
        "slowStartTime": 57808,
        "slowEndTime": 62188
    },
    {
        "text": "As they migrated and settled in new places,...",
        "startTime": 42052,
        "endTime": 44207,
        "slowStartTime": 63228,
        "slowEndTime": 66536
    },
    {
        "text": "...they became isolated from one another and developed in different ways.",
        "startTime": 44387,
        "endTime": 47805,
        "slowStartTime": 66730,
        "slowEndTime": 71932
    },
    {
        "text": "Centuries of living in different conditions, eating different food...",
        "startTime": 48289,
        "endTime": 51397,
        "slowStartTime": 72583,
        "slowEndTime": 77320
    },
    {
        "text": "...and encountering different neighbors turned similar dialects...",
        "startTime": 51554,
        "endTime": 54455,
        "slowStartTime": 77481,
        "slowEndTime": 81907
    },
    {
        "text": "...with varied pronunciation and vocabulary into radically different languages,...",
        "startTime": 54543,
        "endTime": 58528,
        "slowStartTime": 81965,
        "slowEndTime": 88017
    },
    {
        "text": "...continuing to divide as populations grew and spread out further.",
        "startTime": 58811,
        "endTime": 62229,
        "slowStartTime": 88367,
        "slowEndTime": 93568
    },
    {
        "text": "Like genealogists, modern linguists try to map this process...",
        "startTime": 63141,
        "endTime": 66377,
        "slowStartTime": 94862,
        "slowEndTime": 99791
    },
    {
        "text": "...by tracing multiple languages back as far as they can...",
        "startTime": 66463,
        "endTime": 69366,
        "slowStartTime": 99844,
        "slowEndTime": 104274
    },
    {
        "text": "...to their common ancestor or protolanguage.",
        "startTime": 69459,
        "endTime": 71854,
        "slowStartTime": 104338,
        "slowEndTime": 108006
    },
    {
        "text": "A group of all languages related in this way is called a \"language family,\"...",
        "startTime": 72655,
        "endTime": 76382,
        "slowStartTime": 109133,
        "slowEndTime": 114798
    },
    {
        "text": "...which can contain many branches and subfamilies.",
        "startTime": 76675,
        "endTime": 79264,
        "slowStartTime": 115162,
        "slowEndTime": 119121
    },
    {
        "text": "We may never be able to determine how language came about...",
        "startTime": 80365,
        "endTime": 83166,
        "slowStartTime": 120698,
        "slowEndTime": 124974
    },
    {
        "text": "...or whether all human languages did in fact have a common ancestor,...",
        "startTime": 83279,
        "endTime": 86649,
        "slowStartTime": 125069,
        "slowEndTime": 130199
    },
    {
        "text": "...scattered through the babel of migration.",
        "startTime": 86848,
        "endTime": 88887,
        "slowStartTime": 130422,
        "slowEndTime": 133556
    },
    {
        "text": "But the next time you hear a foreign language, pay attention.",
        "startTime": 89319,
        "endTime": 92086,
        "slowStartTime": 134128,
        "slowEndTime": 138354
    },
    {
        "text": "It may not be as foreign as you think.",
        "startTime": 92246,
        "endTime": 94094,
        "slowStartTime": 138519,
        "slowEndTime": 141366
    }
]